            "body": "<pre><code>String [] str = \"1,2,3,4,5\".split(\",\");\nint arrayInt[] = new int[str.length];\nfor (int i = 0; i &lt; str.length; i++) \n    arrayInt[i]=Integer.valueOf(str[i]);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
